# Verify golden snapshots are the executable spec of generated output. Pin them to
# LF on disk so a Windows checkout doesn't introduce CRLF churn that masks a real
# generated-code change inside line-ending noise — snapshot byte-stability also
# underpins sound incremental caching (see .claude/rules/testability.md, performance.md).
#
# Scoped deliberately to snapshots only, to avoid a repo-wide line-ending
# renormalization of source files.
*.verified.cs   text eol=lf
*.verified.txt  text eol=lf
*.received.cs   text eol=lf
*.received.txt  text eol=lf
